ngram\": \"a fad\", \"from\": 721, \"to\": 726}, {\"ngram\": \"its first boom\", \"from\": 734, \"to\": 748}, {\"ngram\": \"the 1960s\", \"from\": 752, \"to\": 761}, {\"ngram\": \"the center\", \"from\": 766, \"to\": 776}, {\"ngram\": \"mainstream youth culture\", \"from\": 780, \"to\": 804}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Skateboarding is as much an art as it is a sport; the fun and freedom of expression bestowed on those willing to step on a board is rewarding for all, regardless of ability, age, gender, socio-economic status, or ethnicity.\", \"from\": 825, \"to\": 1048, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an art\", \"from\": 850, \"to\": 856}, {\"ngram\": \"a sport\", \"from\": 866, \"to\": 873}, {\"ngram\": \"the fun\", \"from\": 875, \"to\": 882}, {\"ngram\": \"freedom\", \"from\": 887, \"to\": 894}, {\"ngram\": \"expression\", \"from\": 898, \"to\": 908}, {\"ngram\": \"a board\", \"from\": 946, \"to\": 953}, {\"ngram\": \"ability\", \"from\": 990, \"to\": 997}, {\"ngram\": \"age\", \"from\": 999, \"to\": 1002}, {\"ngram\": \"gender\", \"from\": 1004, \"to\": 1010}, {\"ngram\": \"socio-economic status\", \"from\": 1012, \"to\": 1033}, {\"ngram\": \"ethnicity\", \"from\": 1038, \"to\": 1047}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Preparations for Paris 2024 World Skate has done a lot of preparation for its second Olympic Games in Paris, following the success of skateboarding's debut in Tokyo 2020, with street and park events.\", \"from\": 1050, \"to\": 1250, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1067, \"end\": 1077, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.8222502588582734e-23, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 1079, \"end\": 1090, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Skate\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"World Skate\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http