1614, \"to\": 1626}, {\"ngram\": \"an amazing show\", \"from\": 1679, \"to\": 1694}, {\"ngram\": \"all the urban sports disciplines\", \"from\": 1737, \"to\": 1769}, {\"ngram\": \"BMX Freestyle\", \"from\": 1787, \"to\": 1800}, {\"ngram\": \"Breaking\", \"from\": 1802, \"to\": 1810}, {\"ngram\": \"Skateboarding Street\", \"from\": 1812, \"to\": 1832}, {\"ngram\": \"Skateboarding Park\", \"from\": 1837, \"to\": 1855}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris 2024 Olympics\", \"from\": 1861, \"to\": 1884}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Maintaining momentum post-Olympics The inclusion of skateboarding in the Olympics has undoubtedly boosted its popularity.\", \"from\": 1887, \"to\": 2009, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"momentum post\", \"from\": 1899, \"to\": 1912}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympics\", \"from\": 1913, \"to\": 1921}, {\"ngram\": \"The inclusion\", \"from\": 1922, \"to\": 1935}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1956, \"to\": 1968}, {\"ngram\": \"its popularity\", \"from\": 1993, \"to\": 2007}]}, {\"sentence\": \"World Skate plans to sustain this momentum through various means.\", \"from\": 2010, \"to\": 2075, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2010, \"end\": 2021, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Skate\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"World Skate\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Skate\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Skate\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this momentum\", \"from\": 2039, \"to\": 2052}, {\"ngram\": \"various means\", \"from\": 2061, \"to\": 2074}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Skateboarding has a history that spans different generations, and today it mainly excites the very young and families.\", \"from\": 2076, \"to\": 2194, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a history\", \"from\": 2094, \"to\": 2103}, {\"ngram\": \"different generations\", \"from\": 2115, \"to\": 2136}, {\"ngram\": \"families\", \"from\": 2185, \"to\": 2193}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Both figures on social media and the number of athletes' followers show a steady growth.\", \"from\": 2195, \"to\": 2283, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Both figures\", \"from\": 2195, \"to\": 2207}, {\"ngram\": \"social media\", \"from\": 2211, \"to\": 2223}, {\"ngram\": \"the number\", \"from\": 2228, \"to\": 2238}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes' followers\", \"from\": 2242, \"to\": 2261}, {\"ngram\": \"a steady growth\", \"from\": 2267, \"to\": 2282}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Our goal is to continue, through the World Skateboarding Tour, to bring this sport to the center of cities, among young people.\", \"from\": 2284, \"to\": 2411, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2327, \"end\": 2340, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Skateboarding\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.9180995246327804e-14, \"text\": \"Skateboarding\", \"types\": [\"Q349\", \"Q1914636\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Skateboarding\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Skateboarding\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Our goal\", \"from\": 2284, \"to\": 2292}, {\"ngram\": \"this sport\", \"from\": 2356, \"to\": 2366}, {\"ngram\": \"the center\", \"from\": 2370, \"to\": 2380}, {\"ngram\": \"cities\", \"from\": 2384, \"to\": 2390}, {\"ngram\": \"young people\", \"from\": 2398, \"to\": 2410}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The competition facilities will be left to the host cities as a legacy for local communities.\", \"from\": 2412, \"to\": 2505, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The competition facilities\", \"from\": 2412, \"to\": 2438}, {\"ngram\": \"the host cities\", \"from\": 2455, \"to\": 2470}, {\"ngram\": \"a legacy\", \"from\": 2474, \"to\": 2482}, {\"ngram\": \"local communities\", \"from\": 2487, \"to\": 2504}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In this way, the sport grows and so does its popularity in every corner of the globe.\", \"from\": 2506, \"to\": 2591, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this way\", \"from\": 2509, \"to\": 2517}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 2519, \"to\": 2528}, {\"ngram\": \"its popularity\", \"from\": 2547, \"to\": 2561}, {\"ngram\": \"every corner\", \"from\": 2565, \"to\": 2577}, {\"ngram\": \"the globe\", \"from\": 2581, \"to\": 2590}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Engaging the youth The accessibility, urban appeal, and inclusivity of skateboarding have contributed to its growing popularity among young people.\", \"from\": 2593, \"to\": 2741, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the youth\", \"from\": 2602, \"to\": 2611}, {\"ngram\": \"The accessibility\", \"from\": 2612, \"to\": 2629}, {\"ngram\": \"urban appeal\", \"from\": 2631, \"to\": 2643}, {\"ngram\": \"inclusivity\", \"from\": 2649, \"to\": 2660}, {\"ngram\": \"its growing popularity\", \"from\": 2698, \"to\": 2720}, {\"ngram\": \"young people\", \"from\": 2727, \"to\": 2739}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Young kids watch the world champions, are inspired by the athletes' skills, and buy skateboards.\", \"from\": 2742, \"to\": 2838, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Young kids\", \"from\": 2742, \"to\": 2752}, {\"ngram\": \"the world champions\", \"from\": 2759, \"to\": 2778}, {\"ngram\": \"the athletes' skills\", \"from\": 2796, \"to\": 2816}, {\"ngram\": \"skateboards\", \"from\": 2826, \"to\": 2837}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They begin to try and train their tricks, and if they have a skatepark near their homes \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0093 in addition to their dedication \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0093 they may become the champions of the future.\", \"from\": 2839, \"to\": 3011, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"their tricks\", \"from\": 2867, \"to\": 2879}, {\"ngram\": \"a skatepark\", \"from\": 2898, \"to\": 2909}, {\"ngram\": \"their homes\", \"from\": 2915, \"to\": 2926}, {\"ngram\": \"addition\", \"from\": 2934, \"to\": 2942}, {\"ngram\": \"their dedication\", \"from\": 2946, \"to\": 2962}, {\"ngram\": \"the champions\", \"from\": 2983, \"to\": 2996}, {\"ngram\": \"the future\", \"from\": 3000, \"to\": 3010}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The skateboarding community is also inclusive and always supportive; skaters support each other and encourage each other.\", \"from\": 3012, \"to\": 3133, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The skateboarding community\", \"from\": 3012, \"to\": 3039}, {\"ngram\": \"skaters\", \"from\": 3081, \"to\": 3088}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It is a sport full of unique values, and this attracts young people and those that observe this sport from the outside.\", \"from\": 3134, \"to\": 3253, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a sport\", \"from\": 3140, \"to\": 3147}, {\"ngram\": \"unique values\", \"from\": 3156, \"to\": 3169}, {\"ngram\": \"young people\", \"from\": 3189, \"to\": 3201}, {\"ngram\": \"this sport\", \"from\": 3225, \"to\": 3235}, {\"ngram\": \"the outside\", \"from\": 3241, \"to\": 3252}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Roos Zwetsloot of the Netherlands competes during the women's street preliminaries of skateboarding at the Olympic Qualifier Series Budapest in Budapest, Hungary, June 21, 2024.\", \"from\": 3255, \"to\": 3432, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3255, \"end\": 3269, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Roos_Zwetsloot\", \"score\": 0.9999988758647257, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Roos Zwetsloot\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Roos_Zwetsloot\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Roos_Zwetsloot\"}, {\"begin\": 3277, \"end\": 3288, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\", \"score\": 0.9999999986844159, \"rank\": 1.3032117750763149e-09, \"text\": \"Netherlands\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\"}, {\"begin\": 3399, \"end\": 3407, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2862679864472299e-14, \"text\": \"Budapest\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\", \"dbpedia\": \"ht